Package: cleanOrgs
Title: Tools for updating NHS organisation codes and adding names
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("John", "Cusack", ,email = "john.cusack@nhs.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to extract and reconcile NHS organisation codes using the ODS API.
    Includes tools to align organisations with their parent ICBs, 
    and to add full and short names for organisations in the South East Region.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
